{"type":"message","id":"03d74472","parentId":"539d9c8a","timestamp":"2026-07-02T01:00:00.215Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Thursday, July 2nd, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-07-02 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1782954000213}}
{"type":"message","id":"c6e1ac51","parentId":"03d74472","timestamp":"2026-07-02T01:02:14.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job notification reminding me of Cursor collaboration rules. The task says \"静默确认即可\" (silent confirmation), meaning I should just confirm receipt without sending a verbose reply.\n\nLet me check the current rules in AGENTS.md to make sure they're consistent with what was just delivered, and confirm I've received this daily reminder.\n\nThe key rules are:\n1. Submit tasks to Cursor via submit_task.py\n2. Handle user confirmations via confirm_write.py\n3. List current tasks via --list\n4. View completed results via --results\n\nThe instruction says \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" - no reply needed, just silently confirm. But this is a cron job that expects a text summary to be returned. The summary should be plain text.\n\nActually, looking at the cron job - it's a \"systemEvent\" that injects text into the session. The cron delivery mode is probably \"announce\" or similar. Since the instruction says \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" and \"Return your summary as plain text\", I should just acknowledge briefly."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>Cursor 协作规则已确认：\n1. 用户要求 Cursor 任务 → submit_task.py --notify\n2. 用户回复确认消息 → confirm_write.py --decision auto\n3. 查看任务队列 → --list\n4. 查看完成结果 → --results\n\n规则已在 AGENTS.md 中，无需重复写入。静默确认完毕。</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782954000214}}
